  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Si el m√©todo del controlador recibe datos, recup√©ralos as√≠:</p>

    <div class="language-php highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kn">use</span> <span class="nc">Illuminate\Http\Request</span><span class="p">;</span>
<span class="mf">...</span>
<span class="k">public</span> <span class="k">function</span> <span class="n">store</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">Request</span> <span class="nv">$request</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="p">{</span> <span class="mf">...</span> <span class="p">}</span>
